org.apache.flex.compiler.definitions

Interface IPackageDefinition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDefinition, IDocumentableDefinition, IMemberedDefinition, IScopedDefinition
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PackageDefinition

    public interface IPackageDefinition
extends IMemberedDefinition
    A definition representing a package declaration.

    An IPackageDefinitionIPackageNode.

    For example, the declaration 

    package flash.display
 {
 }
    creates a package definition whose base name is "display", whose namespace reference is to the public namespace, and whose type reference is null.
